\nHe also urged one and all to observe precaution against the infection, as there was no cure or vaccine against this flu-like infection yet.\n\nHe also emphasized the need for launching awareness about the COVID-19 among the people to stem its spread in the community level.\n\nMinister Dhakal also pledged support from the federal government to state government and local governments while reaffirming that hazard allowances and insurance would be ensured to all the health workers working in forefront till the COVID-19 risks is there.","title":"Health Minister calls for collaboration among three-tier govt to curb COVID-19 - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/03/124602/","video":[]}
